description: South Boston stunner in an A+ location! This spacious 3 bedrooms + office, 3.5 bath home offers nearly 1,900 sq ft of single-level living—perfectly designed for comfort and style. Enjoy rare features like private outdoor space, parking for 2 cars, low HOA fees, and an additional 300 sq ft of climate-controlled storage/flex space. Each bedroom features an en-suite bathroom and ample closet space.  Whether you're working from home, entertaining, or just relaxing, this home checks ALL the boxes!
